               <msContents>
                  <summary/>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i0">
                     <locus from="3v" to="264v">3v-264v</locus>
                     <textLang xml:lang="ar">Arabic</textLang>
                     <title type="apodous lacunous" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT0049IHA#s39IHA">قران, Second half (ǧuz’ 16-30)</title>
                     <incipit xml:lang="ar">
                        <locus target="#3v">-3v</locus>قال الم اقل لك انك لن تستطيع معي صبرا , قال ان سالتك عن شئ بعدها فلا تصاحبني </incipit>
                     <explicit xml:lang="ar">
                        <locus target="#264v">-264v</locus>وانه كان رجال من الانس يعوذون برجال من الجن</explicit>
                     <note>The text begins with verse 18:75 and ends in the middle of the verse 72:6. On some folios the endings and beginnings of the lines are not visible due to tight binding. Words divided into two lines. Vocalized.</note>
                     <note/>
                  </msItem>
               </msContents>
